It is advised that all strictly abide by the following conventions while writing any type of code:
Coding conventions for python:
	http://docs.python-guide.org/en/latest/writing/style/
	More info at:
	https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/
Coding conventions for javascript:
	https://make.wordpress.org/core/handbook/coding-standards/javascript/
	https://google-styleguide.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/javascriptguide.xml#Parentheses
Both for backend and frontend, debuggers need to be discussed
Backend should suggest a code checker tool, if possible
For frontend, JSHint can be used
